        {
            "title": "歐洲評級機構Scope Ratings下調美國信用評級 停擺僵局持續逾三周",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 華盛頓圍繞政府撥款問題陷入僵局逾三周之後，歐洲信用評級機構<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Scope;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Scope\">Scope</a> Ratings把美國的信用評級下調一級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家總部位於柏林的公司表示，對美國這一世界最大經濟體的評級現為AA-。這比該公司的最高評級低三級。該公司在美國政府停擺伊始就曾警告稱，國會陷入僵局對美國評級展望構成風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「公共財政持續惡化和治理標準弱化導致本次下調，」Scope周五在聲明中表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「治理標準的弱化降低了美國政策制定的可預測性，增加了政策失誤風險，並削弱了國會應對結構性財政挑戰的能力，」該機構稱。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0a3cb122-0ed1-3bb8-81c9-603b028a88bf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於美國，Scope的評級比惠譽、穆迪和標普三大對手的評級低兩個級距。該公司加上述三大機構及Morningstar DBRS是歐洲央行用於評估抵押品時僅有的五家公司，Scope是唯一一家總部位於歐洲的機構。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在總統唐納德·川普任內，美國公共財政的路徑正在面臨越來越多的審視，Scope此次評級行動為美國信用記錄再添污點。5月，穆迪的降級使美國失去三大評級機構中最後一個最高評級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Scope早在2023年就將美國評級展望調整為負面，並一直維持至今。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Cut by Scope Ratings After Three Weeks of Shutdown Stalemate</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ezra Fieser.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8Bscope-ratings%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E5%81%9C%E6%93%BA%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%89%E5%91%A8-214443605.html",
